OL,3,CPassengers removed from plane after
OL,4,C'chaos and distressing' incident
OL,6,FFurious passengers have spoken of
OL,7,Ftheir outrage after their EasyJet
OL,8,Fflight to Egypt was cancelled due to a
OL,9,Fgroup of 'drunk and disruptive'
OL,10,Fpassengers.
OL,12,FFootage obtained by UTV shows the
OL,13,Fmoment police boarded the flight to
OL,14,Fthe resort of Hurghada on Saturday on
OL,15,Fthe runway of Belfast International
OL,16,FAirport to remove at least two
OL,17,F"disruptive passengers".
OL,19,FEyewitnesses described the scenes on
OL,20,Fboard as "chaotic and distressing".
