OL,6,FOne passenger told UTV one of those
OL,7,Ftaken off the plane appeared to be
OL,8,Fdrunk. The eyewitness said police
OL,9,Fescorted two people off the plane.
OL,11,FAnother passenger said after waiting
OL,12,Fover 30 hours for the next flight her
OL,13,Ffamily made the decision to go home.
OL,15,FThey said: "The prolonged delays and
OL,16,Fthe police incident caused extreme
OL,17,Fdistress and panic attacks."JWithin
OL,18,Ftheir group was a 72-year-old woman
OL,19,Fwith multiple medical conditions.
