OL,6,FIn a statement, EasyJet added: "Flight
OL,7,FEZY3077 from Belfast to Hurghada on
OL,8,F3rd January was attended by police
OL,9,Fprior to departure due to a group of
OL,10,Fcustomers behaving disruptively
OL,11,Fonboard.
OL,13,F"Our cabin crew are trained to assess
OL,14,Fall situations and to act quickly and
OL,15,Fappropriately to ensure that the
OL,16,Fsafety of the flight and other
OL,17,Fcustomers is not compromised.
