OL,6,F"Unfortunately, this delay led to the
OL,7,Fcrew reaching their safety-regulated
OL,8,Foperating hours, which resulted in the
OL,9,Fflight being rescheduled to operate
OL,10,Fthe following day, and we provided
OL,11,Fcustomers with hotel accommodation and
OL,12,Fmeals.
OL,14,F"The safety and wellbeing of our
OL,15,Fcustomers and crew is always easyJet's
OL,16,Fhighest priority, and while this was
OL,17,Foutside of our control, we are sorry
OL,18,Ffor the inconvenience this will have
